The paper discusses data integration and business intelligence analysis, which are common topics in the database (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The use of schema matching algorithms and Linked Data also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL) techniques. Finally, the paper presents a framework for business users to perform data integration, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category.
